    public final class NetworkUtilizationSampler
extends AbstractSigarSampler
    Logs network utilization of the system, retrieved as NetworkUtilizationRecord via IWriterController.newMonitoringRecord(kieker.common.record.IMonitoringRecord) .

    • 构造器详细资料

      • NetworkUtilizationSampler

        public NetworkUtilizationSampler(org.hyperic.sigar.SigarProxy sigar)
        Constructs a new AbstractSigarSampler with given SigarProxy instance used to retrieve the sensor data. Users should use the factory method SigarSamplerFactory.createSensorNetworkUtilization() to acquire an instance rather than calling this constructor directly.
        参数:
        sigar - The sigar proxy which will be used to retrieve the data.

    • 方法详细资料

      • sample

        public void sample(IMonitoringController monitoringController)
            throws org.hyperic.sigar.SigarException
        Triggers this ISampler to perform a measurement and to pass the data to the given IMonitoringController.
        参数:
        monitoringController - The controller to which the sampler should pass the data.
        抛出:
        org.hyperic.sigar.SigarException
